thread.title: Arizona police release video of fatal self-driving car collision

title: Arizona police release video of fatal self-driving car collision
text:
Arizona police release video of fatal self-driving car collision 6:54am GMT - 00:49 
Police in Arizona on Wednesday release a short video showing the moments leading up to a fatal collision between an Uber self-driving car and a homeless woman who was killed. Jane Lanhee Lee
